dagger.description: Fires standard bullets at all nearby enemies.
dagger.name: dagger

mace.description: Fires streams of flame at all nearby enemies.
mace.name: mace

fortress.description: Fires long-range artillery at ground targets.
fortress.name: fortress

scepter.description: Fires a barrage of charged bullets at all nearby enemies.
scepter.name: scepter

reign.description: Fires a barrage of massive piercing bullets at all nearby enemies.
reign.name: reign

nova.description: Fires laser bolts that damage enemies and repair allied structures. Capable of flight.
nova.name: nova

pulsar.description: Fires arcs of electricity that damage enemies and repair allied structures. Capable of flight.
pulsar.name: pulsar

quasar.description: Fires piercing laser beams that damage enemies and repair allied structures. Capable of flight. Shielded.
quasar.name: quasar

vela.description: Fires a massive continuous laser beam that damages enemies, causes fires and repairs allied structures. Capable of flight.
vela.name: vela

corvus.description: Fires a massive laser blast that damages enemies and repairs allied structures. Can step over most terrain.
corvus.name: corvus

crawler.description: Runs toward enemies and self-destructs, causing a large explosion.
crawler.name: crawler

atrax.description: Fires debilitating orbs of slag at ground targets. Can step over most terrain.
atrax.name: atrax

spiroct.description: Fires sapping laser beams at enemies, repairing itself in the process. Can step over most terrain.
spiroct.name: spiroct

arkyid.description: Fires large sapping laser beams at enemies, repairing itself in the process. Can step over most terrain.
arkyid.name: arkyid

toxopid.description: Fires large electric cluster-shells and piercing lasers at enemies. Can step over most terrain.
toxopid.name: toxopid

flare.description: Fires standard bullets at nearby ground targets.
flare.name: flare

horizon.description: Drops clusters of bombs on ground targets.
horizon.name: horizon

zenith.description: Fires salvos of missiles at all nearby enemies.
zenith.name: zenith

antumbra.description: Fires a barrage of bullets at all nearby enemies.
antumbra.name: antumbra

eclipse.description: Fires two piercing lasers and a barrage of flak at all nearby enemies.
eclipse.name: eclipse

mono.description: Automatically mines copper and lead, depositing it into the core.
mono.name: mono

poly.description: Automatically rebuilds destroyed structures and assists other units in construction.
poly.name: poly

mega.description: Automatically repairs damaged structures. Capable of carrying blocks and small ground units.
mega.name: mega

quad.description: Drops large bombs on ground targets, repairing allied structures and damaging enemies. Capable of carrying medium-sized ground units.
quad.name: quad

oct.description: Protects nearby allies with its regenerating shield. Capable of carrying most ground units.
oct.name: oct

risso.description: Fires a barrage of missiles and bullets at all nearby enemies.
risso.name: risso

minke.description: Fires shells and standard bullets at nearby ground targets.
minke.name: minke

bryde.description: Fires long-range artillery shells and missiles at enemies.
bryde.name: bryde

sei.description: Fires a barrage of missiles and armor-piercing bullets at enemies.
sei.name: sei

omura.description: Fires a long-range piercing railgun bolt at enemies. Constructs flare units.
omura.name: omura

retusa.description: Fires homing torpedoes at nearby enemies. Repairs allied units.
retusa.name: retusa

oxynoe.description: Fires structure-repairing streams of flame at nearby enemies. Targets nearby enemy projectiles with a point defense turret.
oxynoe.name: oxynoe

cyerce.description: Fires seeking cluster-missiles at enemies. Repairs allied units.
cyerce.name: cyerce

aegires.description: Shocks all enemy units and structures that enter its energy field. Repairs all allies.
aegires.name: aegires

navanax.description: Fires explosive EMP projectiles, dealing significant damage to enemy power networks and repairing allied structures. Melts nearby enemies with 4 autonomous laser turrets.
navanax.name: navanax

alpha.description: Defends the Shard core from enemies. Builds structures.
alpha.name: alpha

beta.description: Defends the Foundation core from enemies. Builds structures.
beta.name: beta

gamma.description: Defends the Nucleus core from enemies. Builds structures.
gamma.name: gamma
